snippet.title: Meltan Research Update: Introducing Melmetal!
snippet.description:
The Meltan research continues with Professors Oak and Willow, who appear to have discovered an Evolution—the first of its kind! What could this mean? Here’s the latest. http://bit.ly/2OIrYm6
